victed simply for not voting.</div><div><br></div><div>This is not democracyâ€”this is coercion.</div><div><br></div><div>Itâ€™s time to abolish compulsory voting and let Australians decide for themselves whether they want to participate in elections. A true democracy does not rely on forceâ€”it thrives on voluntary engagement.</div><div><br></div><div>ğŸ”— Join the movement at wendellsdiary.com</div>
